      <p class="about-panel__text">
        Founded in 2018, LEGION Men's Organization is a student-led organization
        at Texas A&amp;M University that aims to develop its members into leaders
        by providing a supportive peer group that encourages personal growth,
        hosting knowledge workshops and events to bolster professional goals,
        participating in community service, and through the support of our
        philanthropic partner.
      </p>

